2 * @mainpage MSP430 DriverLib for MSP430FR2xx_4xx Devices
3 *
4 * @section intro Introduction
5 *
6 * This package provides API documentation for all the peripherals in the MSP430
7 * Driver Library. MSP430 Driver Library provides an easy to use API for
8 * developing applications for the MSP430FR2xx_4xx devices.
9 *
10 * The easiest way to get started is to click on the "Modules" tab above. This will
11 * provide an alphabetical list of peripherals available in the MSP430 Driver
12 * Library.
13 *
14 * This API documentation is broken out into the following sections:
15 * - Documentation Tab
16 * - List of modules contained within this family of Driver Library
17 * - Data Structures Tab
18 * - Data Structures, a list of data structures defined by Driver Library
19 * - Data Fields, a list of fields available in the data structures
20 * - Files Tab
21 * - File List, an alphabetical list of peripheral API's available in MSP430 Driver Library
22 * - Globals, an alphabetical list of MSP430 Driver Library global definitions
23 *
24 * Also note the existence of the following content available on disk. This is not
25 * part of this API but contains useful example code and documentation.
26 *
27 * - Example Code
28 * - under examples/driverlib/MSP430FR2xx_4xx/{peripheral}
29 * - Users Guide
30 * - doc/driverlib/MSP430FR2xx_4xx/MSP430FR2xx_4xx_DriverLib_Users_Guide-2.91.00.20.pdf
31 *
32 */
